p: The MS parameters were set as follows: (1) Full-MS: scan range (m/z) = 350–1500, resolution = 60,000, AGC target = 1e6 and maximum injection time = 50 ms; and (2) PRM: resolution = 15,000, AGC target = 1e5, maximum injection time = 50 ms, loop count = 14; isolation window = 1.6 m/z and NCE = 27%. Skyline software was used for analysis of PRM data.
